channel.title: Compile Broken!
channel.description: Well I put everything all good in my compiler, like everything is fixed but it still wornk work, I put in my jre and tried my jdk and it says that "javac is not a recognized command" or something, what do I do?

item.title: Compile Broken!
item.dc:creator: @dannydude8 dannydude8
item.description:
@dannydude8 wrote:

Ok See This Code

@echo off COLOR 09 title Dannydude8's 1337 Compiler echo ------------------------- "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_18\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

That is what a compiler for JDK version 6 Update 18 should look like.

If you have a diffrent version like V6 Update 16 you change it to this
@echo off
COLOR 09
title Dannydude8’s 1337 Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_16\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause

change the

jdk1.6.0_16

to your version if you dont know your version go into program files and java and see your jdk version
